blic class Student { private String name; private double gpa; private String major; // constructor, getters, toString }","kแบฟt-luแบญn#Kแบฟt luแบญn":"Collection + Stream lร cรดng cแปฅ khรดng thแป thiแบฟu trong Java hiแปn ฤแบกi. Nแบฏm vแปฏng chรบng giรบp bแบกn xแปญ lรฝ dแปฏ liแปu nhanh chรณng, code ngแบฏn gแปn vร dแป bแบฃo trรฌ.\nแป bรi tiแบฟp theo, chรบng ta sแบฝ bรn vแป xแปญ lรฝ ngoแบกi lแป (Exception) vร logging trong Java โ rแบฅt cแบงn thiแบฟt khi แปฉng dแปฅng bแบกn lแปn dแบงn.","mแบนo--best-practices#Mแบนo \u0026amp; Best Practices":"Dรนng Stream ฤแป viแบฟt ngแบฏn gแปn vร dแป ฤแปc; trรกnh side-effects trong map/filter. Dรนng Collectors.toMap() cแบฉn thแบญn khi keys cรณ thแป trรนng โ cแบงn cung cแบฅp merge function. Khi cแบงn performance tuning, ฤo ฤแบกc (benchmark) trฦฐแปc khi chuyแปn sang parallelStream. Sแปญ dแปฅng Optional ฤแป trรกnh NullPointerException khi lแบฅy kแบฟt quแบฃ tแปซ stream.","mแปt-sแป-vรญ-dแปฅ-nรขng-cao#Mแปt sแป vรญ dแปฅ nรขng cao":"","mแป-ฤแบงu#Mแป ฤแบงu":"Khi lแบญp trรฌnh bแบฑng Java, bแบกn sแบฝ rแบฅt thฦฐแปng xuyรชn thao tรกc vแปi tแบญp hแปฃp dแปฏ liแปu โ danh sรกch ngฦฐแปi, tแบญp khรณa, bแบฃng mapping. Java cung cแบฅp Collection Framework ฤแป quแบฃn lรฝ cรกc cแบฅu trรบc nรy, vร Stream API (tแปซ Java 8) ฤแป xแปญ lรฝ dแปฏ liแปu theo phong cรกch hรm, ngแบฏn gแปn vร dแป ฤแปc.\nTrong bรi nรy bแบกn sแบฝ hแปc:\nCรกc collection phแป biแบฟn: List, Set, Map Cรกc thao tรกc cฦก bแบฃn: thรชm, xรณa, tรฌm, duyแปt Stream API: filter, map, sorted, collect, groupingBy, flatMap Vรญ dแปฅ thแปฑc tแบฟ vร cรกch chแบกy","phแบงn-1--cรกc-collection-cฦก-bแบฃn#Phแบงn 1 โ Cรกc Collection cฦก bแบฃn":"","phแบงn-2--duyแปt-vร-thao-tรกc-truyแปn-thแปng-imperative#Phแบงn 2 โ Duyแปt vร thao tรกc truyแปn thแปng (imperative)":"","phแบงn-3--stream-api-phong-cรกch-hรm#Phแบงn 3 โ Stream API (phong cรกch hรm)":"Stream cho phรฉp xแปญ lรฝ tแบญp dแปฏ liแปu theo pipeline: source โ intermediate ops โ terminal op\nVรญ dแปฅ: lแปc, chuyแปn ฤแปi, sแบฏp xแบฟp, thu thแบญp kแบฟt quแบฃ.","sแปญ-dแปฅng-iterator#Sแปญ dแปฅng iterator:":"Iterator\u003cString\u003e it = names.iterator(); while (it.hasNext()) { String n = it.next(); if (n.equals(\"An\")) it.remove(); // xรณa an toรn khi duyแปt }","tham-khแบฃo--ฤแปc-tiแบฟp#Tham khแบฃo \u0026amp; ฤแปc tiแบฟp":"Stream API (Java 8) โ java.util.stream Cรกc Collector hแปฏu รญch: groupingBy, partitioningBy, mapping, summarizingDouble","thแปฑc-hรnh--vรญ-dแปฅ-ฤแบงy-ฤแปง-chแบกy-ฤฦฐแปฃc#Thแปฑc hรnh โ vรญ dแปฅ ฤแบงy ฤแปง (chแบกy ฤฦฐแปฃc)":"","tแบกo-dแปฏ-liแปu-mแบซu-vร-sแปญ-dแปฅng-stream#Tแบกo dแปฏ liแปu mแบซu vร sแปญ dแปฅng Stream:":"List\u003cStudent\u003e students = List.of( new Student(\"An\", 3.2, \"CS\"), new Student(\"Binh\", 2.8, \"IT\"), new Student(\"Chi\", 3.7, \"CS\"), new Student(\"Dung\", 3.5, \"IT\") ); // Lแปc cรกc sinh viรชn GPA \u003e= 3.0, sแบฏp xแบฟp giแบฃm dแบงn theo GPA List\u003cStudent\u003e top = students.stream() .filter(s -\u003e s.getGpa() \u003e= 3.0) .sorted(Comparator.comparingDouble(Student::getGpa).reversed()) .collect(Collectors.toList()); // Nhรณm theo ngรnh vร ฤแบฟm sแป lฦฐแปฃng Map\u003cString, Long\u003e countByMajor = students.stream() .collect(Collectors.groupingBy(Student::getMajor, Collectors.counting()));\rKแบฟt quแบฃ countByMajor cรณ thแป lร {CS=2, IT=2}.","tแบกo-file-examplestreamjava#Tแบกo file ExampleStream.java:":"import java.util.*; import java.util.stream.*; public class ExampleStream { public static void main(String[] args) { List\u003cString\u003e names = Arrays.asList(\"An\",\"Binh\",\"Chi\",\"An\",\"Dung\",\"Huy\"); // 1. distinct + map + sorted List\u003cString\u003e processed = names.stream() .distinct() .map(String::toUpperCase) .sorted() .collect(Collectors.toList()); System.out.println(\"Processed: \" + processed); // 2. filter and count long aCount = names.stream().filter(n -\u003e n.startsWith(\"A\")).count(); System.out.println(\"Start with A: \" + aCount); // 3. grouping example Map\u003cInteger, List\u003cString\u003e\u003e byLength = names.stream() .collect(Collectors.groupingBy(String::length)); System.out.println(\"Grouped by length: \" + byLength); } }","vรญ-dแปฅ-cฦก-bแบฃn#Vรญ dแปฅ cฦก bแบฃn":"import java.util.*; import java.util.stream.*; List\u003cString\u003e names = List.of(\"An\", \"Binh\", \"Chi\", \"An\", \"Dung\"); // Lแปc tรชn khรดng trรนng, chuyแปn thรnh chแปฏ hoa, vร thu vแป List List\u003cString\u003e result = names.stream() .distinct() .map(String::toUpperCase) .collect(Collectors.toList()); System.out.println(result); // [AN, BINH, CHI, DUNG]","vรญ-dแปฅ-dรนng-parallel#Vรญ dแปฅ dรนng parallel:":"long count = bigList.parallelStream().filter(x -\u003e expensiveCheck(x)).count();","vรญ-dแปฅ-thแปฑc-tแบฟ-danh-sรกch-hแปc-sinh-lแปc-vร-nhรณm#Vรญ dแปฅ thแปฑc tแบฟ: danh sรกch hแปc sinh, lแปc vร nhรณm":"","vรญ-dแปฅ-ฤแบงu-ra-cรณ-thแป#Vรญ dแปฅ ฤแบงu ra cรณ thแป:":"Processed: [AN, BINH, CHI, DUNG, HUY]\rStart with A: 2\rGrouped by length: {2=[An], 4=[Binh, Dung, Huy], 3=[Chi]}"},"title":"Hiแปu Collection vร Stream trong Java chแป trong 15 phรบt"},"/blogcuatruc.github.io/blog/bai-3-exception-logging/":{"data":{"":"Giแปi thiแปu\rKhรดng cรณ chฦฐฦกng trรฌnh nรo chแบกy mรฃi mร khรดng lแปi. Dรน bแบกn viแบฟt Java backend, แปฉng dแปฅng mแบกng, hay app desktop, sแปm muแปn gรฌ cลฉng sแบฝ cรณ lแปi xแบฃy ra โ file khรดng tแปn tแบกi, mแบฅt kแบฟt nแปi mแบกng, chia cho 0, lแปi ฤแปnh dแบกng dแปฏ liแปuโฆ\nฤรณ lร lรฝ do Java cung cแบฅp cฦก chแบฟ Exception Handling (xแปญ lรฝ ngoแบกi lแป) ฤแป giรบp chฦฐฦกng trรฌnh:\nKhรดng bแป crash ฤแปt ngแปt Thรดng bรกo lแปi cรณ รฝ nghฤฉa Ghi lแบกi log ฤแป debug sau nรy Phรขn loแบกi Exception trong Java\rNhรณm ฤแบทc ฤiแปm Vรญ dแปฅ Checked Exception Bแบฏt buแปc phแบฃi xแปญ lรฝ (compile-time) IOException, SQLException Unchecked Exception Khรดng bแบฏt buแปc (runtime) NullPointerException, ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException Error Khรดng nรชn xแปญ lรฝ trong code OutOfMemoryError, StackOverflowError ๐ Checked Exception thฦฐแปng dรนng cho cรกc tรฌnh huแปng ngoแบกi cแบฃnh (mแบฅt file, mแบฅt mแบกng).\nUnchecked Exception lร do lแปi lแบญp trรฌnh logic (chia 0, null, index saiโฆ).\nCแบฅu trรบc cฦก bแบฃn try - catch - finally\rCรบ phรกp:\ntry { // Mรฃ cรณ thแป gรขy lแปi } catch (ExceptionType e) { // Xแปญ lรฝ lแปi } finally { // Luรดn chแบกy dรน cรณ lแปi hay khรดng }\rVรญ dแปฅ :\npublic class ExampleTryCatch { public static void main(String[] args) { try { int x = 10 / 0; // lแปi chia cho 0 System.out.println(\"Khรดng bao giแป in tแปi dรฒng nรy\"); } catch (ArithmeticException e) { System.err.println(\"Lแปi: Chia cho 0 khรดng hแปฃp lแป!\"); } finally { System.out.println(\"Luรดn chแบกy khแปi finally.\"); } } }\rKแบฟt quแบฃ:\nLแปi: Chia cho 0 khรดng hแปฃp lแป! Luรดn chแบกy khแปi finally.\rXแปญ lรฝ nhiแปu ngoแบกi lแป\rBแบกn cรณ thแป bแบฏt nhiแปu loแบกi lแปi khรกc nhau trong cรนng khแปi try:\ntry { int[] arr = {1, 2, 3}; System.out.println(arr[5]); // lแปi IndexOutOfBounds int x = 10 / 0; // lแปi Arithmetic } catch (ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException e) { System.err.println(\"Truy cแบญp mแบฃng sai vแป trรญ!\"); } catch (ArithmeticException e) { System.err.println(\"Lแปi chia cho 0!\"); } catch (Exception e) { System.err.println(\"Lแปi khรดng xรกc ฤแปnh: \" + e.getMessage()); }\rLฦฐu รฝ: luรดn ฤแบทt catch (Exception e) cuแปi cรนng, vรฌ nรณ bao hรm tแบฅt cแบฃ lแปi con.\nNรฉm vร tแบกo Exception tรนy chแปnh","best-practices#Best Practices":"Khรดng nรชn ฤแป catch (Exception e) mร khรดng xแปญ lรฝ gรฌ. Ghi log cรณ ngแปฏ cแบฃnh rรต rรng (logger.log(Level.SEVERE, \"Lแปi khi ฤแปc file\", e)). Dรนng framework logging chuyรชn nghiแปp hฦกn khi dแปฑ รกn lแปn: SLF4J, Log4j2, Lombok @Slf4j. Vแปi แปฉng dแปฅng mแบกng: log ฤแปa chแป IP client, thแปi gian, loแบกi request ฤแป dแป truy vแบฟt.","bรi-tiแบฟp-theo#Bรi tiแบฟp theo":"โLแบญp trรฌnh Socket cฦก bแบฃn trong Javaโ โ bแบกn sแบฝ hแปc cรกch tแบกo client-server vร gแปญi dแปฏ liแปu giแปฏa hai mรกy tรญnh.","bรi-tแบญp-gแปฃi-รฝ#Bรi tแบญp gแปฃi รฝ":"Viแบฟt chฦฐฦกng trรฌnh ฤฤng nhแบญp: nแบฟu ngฦฐแปi dรนng nhแบญp sai mแบญt khแบฉu 3 lแบงn, nรฉm Exception TooManyAttemptsException. Tแบกo file log.txt vร ghi log khi ngฦฐแปi dรนng thแปฑc hiแปn thao tรกc (login, logout, thแบฅt bแบกi). Sแปญ dแปฅng try-with-resources ฤแป ฤแบฃm bแบฃo file luรดn ฤฦฐแปฃc ฤรณng.","cแบฅp-ฤแป-log-phแป-biแบฟn#Cแบฅp ฤแป Log phแป biแบฟn":"Cแบฅp ฤแป ร nghฤฉa SEVERE Lแปi nghiรชm trแปng, cแบงn can thiแปp WARNING Cแบฃnh bรกo tiแปm แบฉn INFO Thรดng tin chung CONFIG Thรดng tin cแบฅu hรฌnh FINE / FINER / FINEST Dรนng khi debug chi tiแบฟt","cแบฅu-trรบc-cฦก-bแบฃn-try---catch---finally#Cแบฅu trรบc cฦก bแบฃn try - catch - finally":"","dรนng-throw-ฤแป-nรฉm-lแปi-thแปง-cรดng#Dรนng throw ฤแป nรฉm lแปi thแปง cรดng:":"public void checkAge(int age) { if (age \u003c 18) throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"Chฦฐa ฤแปง 18 tuแปi!\"); System.out.println(\"ฤแปง tuแปi truy cแบญp.\"); }","ghi-log-ra-file#Ghi log ra file":"try { FileHandler fh = new FileHandler(\"app.log\", true); logger.addHandler(fh); fh.setFormatter(new SimpleFormatter()); logger.info(\"Ghi log ra file app.log thรnh cรดng!\"); } catch (Exception e) { e.printStackTrace(); }\rSau khi chแบกy, bแบกn sแบฝ thแบฅy file app.log chแปฉa toรn bแป lแปch sแปญ log cแปงa แปฉng dแปฅng.","giแปi-thiแปu#Giแปi thiแปu":"","kแบฟt-quแบฃ-console#Kแบฟt quแบฃ (console):":"Thg 10 23, 2025 10:15:00 SA LoggingDemo main\rINFO: แปจng dแปฅng bแบฏt ฤแบงu...\rThg 10 23, 2025 10:15:00 SA LoggingDemo main\rSEVERE: Lแปi toรกn hแปc xแบฃy ra\rjava.lang.ArithmeticException: / by zero\r...\rWARNING: แปจng dแปฅng kแบฟt thรบc vแปi cแบฃnh bรกo.","logging-trong-java-javautillogging#Logging trong Java (java.util.logging)":"Khi แปฉng dแปฅng lแปn, bแบกn khรดng thแป chแป System.out.println() ฤแป xem lแปi. Thay vรo ฤรณ, dรนng logging framework ฤแป:\nGhi log ra file, console, hoแบทc server Gแบฏn cแบฅp ฤแป log: INFO, W