trong file readfile.log.","vรญ-dแปฅ-ฤฦกn-giแบฃn#Vรญ dแปฅ ฤฦกn giแบฃn:":"import java.util.logging.*; public class LoggingDemo { private static final Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(LoggingDemo.class.getName()); public static void main(String[] args) { logger.info(\"แปจng dแปฅng bแบฏt ฤแบงu...\"); try { int x = 10 / 0; } catch (ArithmeticException e) { logger.log(Level.SEVERE, \"Lแปi toรกn hแปc xแบฃy ra\", e); } logger.warning(\"แปจng dแปฅng kแบฟt thรบc vแปi cแบฃnh bรกo.\"); } }","xแปญ-lรฝ-nhiแปu-ngoแบกi-lแป#Xแปญ lรฝ nhiแปu ngoแบกi lแป":""},"title":"Xแปญ lรฝ ngoแบกi lแป vร Logging trong Java"},"/blogcuatruc.github.io/blog/bai-4-java-socket-basic/":{"data":{"":"","bรi-tiแบฟp-theo#Bรi tiแบฟp theo":"โXรขy dแปฑng แปฉng dแปฅng chat nhiแปu client vแปi ฤa luแปng trong Javaโ (bแบกn sแบฝ hแปc cรกch mแปi client cรณ mแปt luแปng riรชng ฤแป giao tiแบฟp song song vแปi server!)","bรi-tแบญp-mแป-rแปng#Bรi tแบญp mแป rแปng":"Viแบฟt chฦฐฦกng trรฌnh chat 2 chiแปu giแปฏa client vร server. Tแบกo server cho phรฉp nhiแปu client kแบฟt nแปi cรนng lรบc (gแปฃi รฝ: sแปญ dแปฅng Thread). Ghi log cรกc tin nhแบฏn client gแปญi vรo file chat.log.","client-console#Client console:":"Kแบฟt nแปi tแปi server thรnh cรดng!\rPhแบฃn hแปi tแปซ Server: Chรo Client! Tรดi ฤรฃ nhแบญn ฤฦฐแปฃc tin nhแบฏn cแปงa bแบกn.","cรกch-chแบกy-thแปญ#Cรกch chแบกy thแปญ":"Mแป hai cแปญa sแป terminal.\nTrong cแปญa sแป thแปฉ nhแบฅt, chแบกy Server:\njavac SimpleServer.java java SimpleServer\rTrong cแปญa sแป thแปฉ hai, chแบกy Client:\njavac SimpleClient.java java SimpleClient\rQuan sรกt:\nServer hiแปn thแป tin nhแบฏn nhแบญn tแปซ Client Client nhแบญn phแบฃn hแปi tแปซ Server","cรกch-hoแบกt-ฤแปng#Cรกch hoแบกt ฤแปng":"Server tแบกo ServerSocket(port) โ luรดn โlแบฏng ngheโ tแบกi cแปng ฤรณ. Client tแบกo Socket(host, port) โ yรชu cแบงu kแบฟt nแปi. Khi kแบฟt nแปi thรnh cรดng, Server nhแบญn ฤฦฐแปฃc Socket riรชng cho client. Hai bรชn cรณ thแป gแปญi vร nhแบญn dแปฏ liแปu qua luแปng I/O.","giแปi-thiแปu#Giแปi thiแปu":"Lแบญp trรฌnh mแบกng (Network Programming) lร mแปt phแบงn quan trแปng trong Java.\nNรณ cho phรฉp cรกc chฦฐฦกng trรฌnh giao tiแบฟp qua Internet hoแบทc mแบกng LAN, vรญ dแปฅ nhฦฐ:\nChat app Web server แปจng dแปฅng truyแปn file Hแป thแปng giao tiแบฟp IoT Java hแป trแปฃ mแบกng rแบฅt mแบกnh thรดng qua Socket API โ lแปp nแบฑm trong package java.net.","khรกi-niแปm-cฦก-bแบฃn-vแป-socket#Khรกi niแปm cฦก bแบฃn vแป Socket":"Socket lร ฤiแปm cuแปi (endpoint) cแปงa kแบฟt nแปi hai chiแปu giแปฏa hai tiแบฟn trรฌnh (process) qua mแบกng.\nMรด hรฌnh ฤฦกn giแบฃn:\ngraph LR\rClient \u003c--\u003e Server\rVai trรฒ Nhiแปm vแปฅ ServerSocket Chแป (listen) yรชu cแบงu kแบฟt nแปi tแปซ client Socket ฤแบกi diแปn cho kแบฟt nแปi giแปฏa client vร server InputStream / OutputStream Dรนng ฤแป ฤแปc / ghi dแปฏ liแปu","kแบฟt-quแบฃ-mแบซu#Kแบฟt quแบฃ mแบซu":"","mแปt-vรi-lฦฐu-รฝ#Mแปt vรi lฦฐu รฝ":"Cแปng (port) thฦฐแปng chแปn tแปซ 1024 โ 65535 (trรกnh trรนng vแปi dแปch vแปฅ hแป thแปng). Nแบฟu bแบกn chแบกy nhiแปu lแบงn mร bรกo lแปi โAddress already in useโ, chแป vรi giรขy hoแบทc ฤแปi cแปng khรกc (vรญ dแปฅ 8081). Dรนng try-with-resources ฤแป tแปฑ ฤแปng ฤรณng socket sau khi dรนng. Trong lแบญp trรฌnh mแบกng thแปฑc tแบฟ, luรดn cแบงn xแปญ lรฝ Timeout, Multi-threading, vร Error Logging.","phรขn-tรญch-luแปng-hoแบกt-ฤแปng#Phรขn tรญch luแปng hoแบกt ฤแปng":"Bฦฐแปc Thแปฑc hiแปn Mรด tแบฃ 1 new ServerSocket(8080) Mแป cแปng vร chแป kแบฟt nแปi 2 serverSocket.accept() Chแป client 3 new Socket(\"localhost\",8080) Client gแปญi yรชu cแบงu 4 Hai bรชn trao ฤแปi dแปฏ liแปu qua InputStream \u0026 OutputStream","server-console#Server console:":"Server ฤang lแบฏng nghe tแบกi cแปng 8080...\rKแบฟt nแปi tแปซ client: /127.0.0.1\rClient gแปญi: Xin chรo Server!","sฦก-ฤแป-minh-hแปa#Sฦก ฤแป minh hแปa:":"sequenceDiagram\rparticipant C as Client\rparticipant S as Server\rS-\u003e\u003eS: ServerSocket(8080)\rNote right of S: Chแป kแบฟt nแปi...\rC-\u003e\u003eS: Socket(\"localhost\",8080)\rS-\u003e\u003eC: Kแบฟt nแปi thรnh cรดng!\rC-\u003e\u003eS: Gแปญi \"Xin chรo Server!\"\rS-\u003e\u003eC: Gแปญi \"Chรo Client, tรดi ฤรฃ nhแบญn ฤฦฐแปฃc!\"","tแปng-kแบฟt#Tแปng kแบฟt":"ServerSocket dรนng cho phรญa server ฤแป chแป kแบฟt nแปi. Socket dรนng cho client hoแบทc mแปi kแบฟt nแปi server-client. Giao tiแบฟp dแปฑa trรชn luแปng dแปฏ liแปu (I/O Stream). ฤรขy lร nแปn tแบฃng ฤแป phรกt triแปn แปฉng dแปฅng mแบกng, game online, hoแบทc API thแปง cรดng.","vรญ-dแปฅ-1-server-ฤฦกn-giแบฃn#Vรญ dแปฅ 1: Server ฤฦกn giแบฃn":"// File: SimpleServer.java import java.io.*; import java.net.*; public class SimpleServer { public static void main(String[] args) { try (ServerSocket serverSocket = new ServerSocket(8080)) { System.out.println(\"Server ฤang lแบฏng nghe tแบกi cแปng 8080...\"); Socket socket = serverSocket.accept(); System.out.println(\"Kแบฟt nแปi tแปซ client: \" + socket.getInetAddress()); BufferedReader in = new BufferedReader( new InputStreamReader(socket.getInputStream())); PrintWriter out = new PrintWriter(socket.getOutputStream(), true); String message = in.readLine(); System.out.println(\"Client gแปญi: \" + message); out.println(\"Chรo Client! Tรดi ฤรฃ nhแบญn ฤฦฐแปฃc tin nhแบฏn cแปงa bแบกn.\"); socket.close(); } catch (IOException e) { System.err.println(\"Lแปi server: \" + e.getMessage()); } } }","vรญ-dแปฅ-2-client-kแบฟt-nแปi-tแปi-server#Vรญ dแปฅ 2: Client kแบฟt nแปi tแปi Server":"// File: SimpleClient.java import java.io.*; import java.net.*; public class SimpleClient { public static void main(String[] args) { try (Socket socket = new Socket(\"localhost\", 8080)) { System.out.println(\"Kแบฟt nแปi tแปi server thรnh cรดng!\"); BufferedReader in = new BufferedReader( new InputStreamReader(socket.getInputStream())); PrintWriter out = new PrintWriter(socket.getOutputStream(), true); out.println(\"Xin chรo Server!\"); String response = in.readLine(); System.out.println(\"Phแบฃn hแปi tแปซ Server: \" + response); } catch (IOException e) { System.err.println(\"Lแปi client: \" + e.getMessage()); } } }"},"title":"Lแบญp trรฌnh Socket cฦก bแบฃn trong Java"},"/blogcuatruc.github.io/blog/bai-5-da-luong/":{"data":{"1-giแปi-thiแปu-thread--runnable#1. Giแปi thiแปu Thread \u0026amp; Runnable":"Trong Java, mแปi Thread lร mแปt luแปng xแปญ lรฝ riรชng biแปt.\nKhi cรณ nhiแปu client cรนng kแบฟt nแปi, ta dรนng nhiแปu luแปng ฤแป server xแปญ lรฝ song song, trรกnh tรฌnh trแบกng โnghแบฝnโ.\nVรญ dแปฅ ฤฦกn giแบฃn:\nclass MyThread extends Thread { public void run() { System.out.println(\"Luแปng ฤang chแบกy: \" + Thread.currentThread().getName()); } } public class DemoThread { public static void main(String[] args) { for (int i = 1; i \u003c= 3; i++) { new MyThread().start(); } } }\rKแบฟt quแบฃ: Chฦฐฦกng trรฌnh in ra 3 luแปng chแบกy gแบงn nhฦฐ cรนng lรบc.","2-xรขy-dแปฑng-server-ฤa-luแปng#2. Xรขy dแปฑng Server ฤa luแปng":"","3-cรกch-chแบกy-thแปญ#3. Cรกch chแบกy thแปญ":"Mแป nhiแปu cแปญa sแป terminal (1 server + 2 hoแบทc 3 client).\nTrong cแปญa sแป 1 (Server):\njavac ChatServer.java java ChatServer\rTrong cแปญa sแป 2 (Client 1):\njavac ChatClient.java java ChatClient\rTrong cแปญa sแป 3 (Client 2):\njava ChatClient","4-phรขn-tรญch-hoแบกt-ฤแปng#4. Phรขn tรญch hoแบกt ฤแปng":"Bฦฐแปc Thแปฑc hiแปn Mรด tแบฃ 1 new ServerSocket(8080) Mแป cแปng lแบฏng nghe 2 serverSocket.accept() Chแป client kแบฟt nแปi 3 Mแปi client โ new Thread Xแปญ lรฝ song song 4 broadcast() Gแปญi tin nhแบฏn tแปi tแบฅt cแบฃ client ฤang kแบฟt nแปi","5-lฦฐu-รฝ--mแป-rแปng#5. Lฦฐu รฝ \u0026amp; mแป rแปng":"Dรนng synchronized ฤแป trรกnh xung ฤแปt khi nhiแปu luแปng ghi dแปฏ liแปu. Cรณ thแป thรชm tรชn ngฦฐแปi dรนng (username) ฤแป hiแปn thแป ฤแบนp hฦกn. Cรณ thแป nรขng cแบฅp lรชn GUI Chat App vแปi Swing hoแบทc JavaFX. ฤแป server hแป trแปฃ ngแบฏt kแบฟt nแปi mแปm, cแบงn thรชm socket.close() ฤรบng cรกch.","bรi-5-giao-tiแบฟp-ฤa-luแปng-trong-lแบญp-trรฌnh-mแบกng-java#Bรi 5: Giao tiแบฟp ฤa luแปng trong lแบญp trรฌnh mแบกng Java":"Bรi 5: Giao tiแบฟp ฤa luแปng trong lแบญp trรฌnh mแบกng Java","bรi-tiแบฟp-theo#Bรi tiแบฟp theo":"โGiao tiแบฟp Server โ Client bแบฑng Object Stream (truyแปn ฤแปi tฦฐแปฃng trong Java)โ","bรi-tแบญp-mแป-rแปng#Bรi tแบญp mแป rแปng":"Thรชm tรญnh nฤng ฤแบทt tรชn ngฦฐแปi dรนng khi client kแบฟt nแปi. Ghi lแบกi toรn bแป tin nhแบฏn vรo file chat.log. Nรขng cแบฅp giao diแปn bแบฑng Swing: tแบกo cแปญa sแป chat, danh sรกch ngฦฐแปi online. Tแบกo โPrivate Chatโ โ gแปญi tin nhแบฏn riรชng cho tแปซng client.","client-1#Client 1:":"Chรo bแบกn! Nhแบญp 'exit' ฤแป thoรกt.\rNgฦฐแปi dรนng: Ai ฤang แป ฤรขy khรดng?\rNgฦฐแปi dรนng: Mรฌnh ฤรขy nรจ!","client-2#Client 2:":"Chรo bแบกn! Nhแบญp 'exit' ฤแป thoรกt.\rNgฦฐแปi dรนng: Xin chรo!\rNgฦฐแปi dรนng: Ai ฤang แป ฤรขy khรดng?","clientjava#Client.java":"import java.io.*; import java.net.*; public class ChatClient { public static void main(String[] args) { try (Socket socket = new Socket(\"localhost\", 8080); BufferedReader in = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(socket.getInputStream())); PrintWriter out = new PrintWriter(socket.getOutputStream(), true); BufferedReader userInput = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(System.in))) { System.out.println(\"ฤรฃ kแบฟt nแปi tแปi server chat!\"); new Thread(() -\u003e { try { String serverMsg; while ((serverMsg = in.readLine()) != null) { System.out.println(serverMsg); } } catch (IOException e) { System.out.println(\"Mแบฅt kแบฟt nแปi tแปi server.\"); } }).start(); String input; while ((input = userInput.readLine()) != null) { out.println(input); if (input.equalsIgnoreCase(\"exit\")) break; } } catch (IOException e) { System.out.println(\"Khรดng thแป kแบฟt nแปi tแปi server.\"); } } }","kแบฟt-quแบฃ-mแบซu#Kแบฟt quแบฃ mแบซu":"","mแปฅc-tiรชu#Mแปฅc tiรชu":"Mแป rแปng แปฉng dแปฅng mแบกng ฤแป cho phรฉp nhiแปu client kแบฟt nแปi vร trรฒ chuyแปn song song vแปi nhau.","nแปi-dung-chรญnh#Nแปi dung chรญnh":"Giแปi thiแปu Thread vร Runnable trong Java Tแบกo Server ฤa luแปng (Multi-threaded Server) Quแบฃn lรฝ nhiแปu client cรนng lรบc Minh hแปa: แปจng dแปฅng Chat mini nhฦฐ Messenger","server-console#Server console:":"Server chat ฤang chแบกy trรชn cแปng 8080...\rKแบฟt nแปi mแปi tแปซ: /127.0.0.1\rTแปซ client: Xin chรo!\rTแปซ client: Ai ฤang แป ฤรขy khรดng?","serverjava#Server.java":"import java.io.*; import java.net.*; import java.util.*; public class ChatServer { private static final int PORT = 8080; private static Set\u003cPrintWriter\u003e clientWriters = new HashSet\u003c\u003e(); public static void main(String[] args) { System.out.println(\"Server chat ฤang chแบกy trรชn cแปng \" + PORT + \"...\"); try (ServerSocket serverSocket = new ServerSocket(PORT)) { while (true) { Socket clientSocket = serverSocket.accept(); System.out.println(\"Kแบฟt nแปi mแปi tแปซ: \" + clientSocket.getInetAddress()); new ClientHandler(clientSocket).start(); } } catch (IOException e) { e.printStackTrace(); } } static class ClientHandler extends Thread { private Socket socket; private PrintWriter out; private BufferedReader in; public ClientHandler(Socket socket) { this.socket = socket; } public void run() { try { in = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(socket.getInputStream())); out = new PrintWriter(socket.getOutputStream(), true); synchronized (clientWriters) { clientWriters.add(out); } out.println(\"Chรo bแบกn! Nhแบญp 'exit' ฤแป thoรกt.\"); String message; while ((message = in.readLine()) != null) { if (message.equalsIgnoreCase(\"exit\")) break; System.out.println(\"Tแปซ client: \" + message); broadcast(\"Ngฦฐแปi dรนng: \" + message); } } catch (IOException e) { System.out.println(\"Lแปi kแบฟt nแปi client.\"); } finally { try { socket.close(); } catch (IOException e) {} synchronized (clientWriters) { clientWriters.remove(out); } System.out.println(\"Mแปt client ฤรฃ ngแบฏt kแบฟt nแปi.\"); } } private void broadcast(String message) { synchronized (clientWriters) { for (PrintWriter writer : clientWriters) { writer.println(message); } } } } }","tแปng-kแบฟt#Tแปng kแบฟt":"ServerSocket lแบฏng nghe kแบฟt nแปi. Mแปi client โ mแปt Thread xแปญ lรฝ riรชng biแปt. synchronized ฤแบฃm bแบฃo an toรn dแปฏ liแปu khi nhiแปu luแปng truy cแบญp. ฤรขy lร nแปn tแบฃng cแปงa cรกc แปฉng dแปฅng chat ฤa ngฦฐแปi dรนng, game online, hoแบทc hแป thแปng giao tiแบฟp theo thแปi gian thแปฑc.","รฝ-tฦฐแปng#ร tฦฐแปng":"Mแปi khi cรณ client kแบฟt nแปi โ Server tแบกo mแปt luแปng riรชng ฤแป giao tiแบฟp vแปi client ฤรณ. Cรกc client gแปญi tin nhแบฏn, server sแบฝ phรกt lแบกi (broadcast) cho tแบฅt cแบฃ nhแปฏng client khรกc."},"title":"Tแบกo server ฤa luแปng bแบฑng Java โ Chat nhiแปu ngฦฐแปi nhฦฐ Messenger mini"},"/blogcuatruc.github.io/blog/bai-6-ket-noi-java-voi-mysql/":{"data":{"":"","1-cรi-ฤแบทt-mysql#1. Cรi ฤแบทt MySQL":"Tแบฃi vร cรi ฤแบทt MySQL Server + MySQL Workbench. Tแบกo cฦก sแป dแปฏ liแปu vรญ dแปฅ: CREATE DATABASE chat_app; USE chat_app; CREATE TABLE users ( id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY, username VARCHAR(50), message TEXT );","1-thรชm-dแปฏ-liแปu-insert#1. Thรชm dแปฏ liแปu (INSERT)":"import java.sql.*; public class InsertUser { public static void main(String[] args) { String url = \"jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/chat_app\"; String user = \"root\"; String password = \"123456\"; String sql = \"INSERT INTO users (username, message) VALUES (?, ?)\"; try (Connection conn = DriverManager.getConnection(url, user, password); PreparedStatement stmt = conn.prepareStatement(sql)) { stmt.setString(1, \"Nguyen\"); stmt.setString(2, \"Xin chรo mแปi ngฦฐแปi!\"); int rows = stmt.executeUpdate(); if (rows \u003e 0) { System.out.println(\"Thรชm dแปฏ liแปu thรnh cรดng!\"); } } catch (SQLException e) { e.printStackTrace(); } } }","2-cรi-ฤแบทt-mysql-connector#2. Cรi ฤแบทt MySQL Connector":"Nแบฟu dรนng Maven, thรชm dependency vรo pom.xml:\nmysql mysql-connector-java 8.1.0 Nแบฟu chแบกy bแบฑng tay, tแบฃi file .jar tแบกi https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/connector/j/ vร thรชm vรo classpath cแปงa project.","2-truy-xuแบฅt-dแปฏ-liแปu-select#2. Truy xuแบฅt dแปฏ liแปu (SELECT)":"import java.sql.*; public class SelectUser { public static void main(String[] args) { String url = \"jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/chat_app\"; String user = \"root\"; String password = \"123456\"; String sql = \"SELECT id, username, message FROM users\"; try (Connection conn = DriverManager.getConnection(url, user, password); PreparedStatement stmt = conn.prepareStatement(sql); ResultSet rs = stmt.executeQuery()) { while (rs.next()) { int id = rs.getInt(\"id\"); String username = rs.getString(\"username\"); String message = rs.getString(\"message\"); System.out.println(id + \" | \" + username + \" | \" + message); } } catch (SQLException e) { e.printStackTrace(); } } }","bแบฏt-ฤแบงu-nรo#Bแบฏt ฤแบงu nรo!":"Trong cรกc แปฉng dแปฅng Java, viแปc lฦฐu trแปฏ vร truy xuแบฅt dแปฏ liแปu thฦฐแปng ฤฦฐแปฃc thแปฑc hiแปn thรดng qua cฦก sแป dแปฏ liแปu. JDBC (Java Database Connectivity) lร API tiรชu chuแบฉn giรบp Java kแบฟt nแปi vร giao tiแบฟp vแปi nhiแปu hแป quแบฃn trแป cฦก sแป dแปฏ liแปu khรกc nhau, chแบณng hแบกn nhฦฐ MySQL.\nBรi viแบฟt nรy sแบฝ hฦฐแปng dแบซn bแบกn tแปซ cฦก bแบฃn ฤแบฟn thแปฑc hรnh cรกch kแบฟt nแปi Java vแปi MySQL vร thแปฑc hiแปn truy vแบฅn dแปฏ liแปu.\nBแบกn sแบฝ hแปc ฤฦฐแปฃc:\nCแบฅu trรบc vร thรnh phแบงn cแปงa JDBC Cรกch kแบฟt nแปi Java vแปi MySQL Thแปฑc hiแปn cรกc thao tรกc cฦก bแบฃn: SELECT, INSERT Vรญ dแปฅ lฦฐu thรดng tin ngฦฐแปi dรนng hoแบทc lแปch sแปญ chat","cรกch-1-chแบกy-trong-ide-netbeans-intellij-eclipse#Cรกch 1: Chแบกy trong IDE (NetBeans, IntelliJ, Eclipse)":"Mแป IDE Tแบกo Project Java Thรชm mysql-connector-java.jar vรo Libraries Biรชn dแปch vร chแบกy file .java","cรกch-2-chแบกy-bแบฑng-dรฒng-lแปnh#Cรกch 2: Chแบกy bแบฑng dรฒng lแปnh":"javac ConnectMySQL.java java -cp .;mysql-connector-java-8.1.0.jar ConnectMySQL","cแบฅu-trรบc-jdbc-gแปm-4-thรnh-phแบงn-chรญnh#Cแบฅu trรบc JDBC gแปm 4 thรnh phแบงn chรญnh:":"Driver โ Cแบงu nแปi giแปฏa Java vร hแป quแบฃn trแป CSDL\nVรญ dแปฅ: MySQL cรณ driver riรชng lร mysql-connector-java.jar.\nConnection โ ฤแบกi diแปn cho mแปt kแบฟt nแปi tแปi cฦก sแป dแปฏ liแปu.\nStatement / PreparedStatement โ Dรนng ฤแป gแปญi cรกc cรขu lแปnh SQL.\nResultSet โ Chแปฉa kแบฟt quแบฃ trแบฃ vแป khi thแปฑc hiแปn cรขu lแปnh SELECT.\nSฦก ฤแป hoแบกt ฤแปng:\ngraph LR\rA[Java Application] --\u003e B[JDBC API]\rB --\u003e C[JDBC Driver]\rC --\u003e D[Database MySQL]","giแบฃi-thรญch#Giแบฃi thรญch:":"DriverManager.getConnection(...): tแบกo ฤแปi tฦฐแปฃng Connection. jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/chat_app: ฤแปnh nghฤฉa ฤฦฐแปng dแบซn JDBC ฤแบฟn CSDL MySQL. ฤแปซng quรชn conn.close() ฤแป ฤรณng kแบฟt nแปi.","kแบฟt-luแบญn#Kแบฟt luแบญn":"Thรดng qua JDBC, Java cรณ thแป dแป dรng kแบฟt nแปi vแปi MySQL vร thแปฑc hiแปn cรกc thao tรกc vแปi dแปฏ liแปu nhฦฐ thรชm, ฤแปc, sแปญa, xรณa. Viแปc hiแปu rรต cรกch hoแบกt ฤแปng cแปงa JDBC lร nแปn tแบฃng quan trแปng ฤแป hแปc cรกc cรดng nghแป nรขng cao hฦกn nhฦฐ Hibernate hoแบทc JPA.","phแบงn-1--tแปng-quan-vแป-jdbc#Phแบงn 1 โ Tแปng quan vแป JDBC":"JDBC lร mแปt giao diแปn lแบญp trรฌnh แปฉng dแปฅng (API) giรบp Java cรณ thแป:\nKแบฟt nแปi vแปi cฦก sแป dแปฏ liแปu (MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQL Server, v.v.) Gแปญi vร thแปฑc thi cรกc lแปnh SQL (SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE) Nhแบญn kแบฟt quแบฃ trแบฃ vแป tแปซ cฦก sแป dแปฏ liแปu","phแบงn-2--chuแบฉn-bแป-mรดi-trฦฐแปng#Phแบงn 2 โ Chuแบฉn bแป mรดi trฦฐแปng":"","phแบงn-3--kแบฟt-nแปi-mysql-bแบฑng-jdbc#Phแบงn 3 โ Kแบฟt nแปi MySQL bแบฑng JDBC":"Dฦฐแปi ฤรขy lร vรญ dแปฅ Java cฦก bแบฃn ฤแป kiแปm tra kแบฟt nแปi thรnh cรดng.\nimport java.sql.Connection; import java.sql.DriverManager; import java.sql.SQLException; public class ConnectMySQL { public static void main(String[] args) { String url = \"jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/chat_app\"; String user = \"root\"; String password = \"1234