su-kien/":{"data":{"1-dom-lร-gรฌ#1. DOM lร gรฌ?":"Khi trรฌnh duyแปt tแบฃi mแปt trang HTML, nรณ sแบฝ biแบฟn toรn bแป cแบฅu trรบc cแปงa trang ฤรณ thรnh cรขy DOM (Document Object Model).\nDOM khรดng chแป lร โnแปi dungโ mร cรฒn lร โmรด hรฌnh dแปฏ liแปuโ ฤแป JavaScript truy cแบญp, sแปญa ฤแปi, hoแบทc thรชm mแปi phแบงn tแปญ.","2-truy-cแบญp-phแบงn-tแปญ-html#2. Truy cแบญp phแบงn tแปญ HTML":"","3-thay-ฤแปi-nแปi-dung-vร-thuแปc-tรญnh#3. Thay ฤแปi nแปi dung vร thuแปc tรญnh":"JavaScript cho phรฉp bแบกn thay ฤแปi nแปi dung, mรu sแบฏc, hoแบทc thรชm class cho phแบงn tแปญ.\nconst box = document.getElementById(\"title\"); box.textContent = \"Chรo mแปซng ฤแบฟn vแปi DOM!\"; box.style.backgroundColor = \"lightcoral\"; box.style.padding = \"10px\";\rKแบฟt quแบฃ: phแบงn tแปญ ฤแปi nแปi dung vร cรณ nแปn mรu ฤแป nhแบกt.","4-sแปฑ-kiแปn-event-trong-javascript#4. Sแปฑ kiแปn (Event) trong JavaScript":"Sแปฑ kiแปn lร bแบฅt kแปณ hรnh ฤแปng nรo ngฦฐแปi dรนng thแปฑc hiแปn: nhแบฅp chuแปt, nhแบญp dแปฏ liแปu, rรช chuแปt, cuแปn trangโฆ","5-vรญ-dแปฅ-nรบt-ฤแปi-mรu-nแปn#5. Vรญ dแปฅ: Nรบt ฤแปi mรu nแปn":"","6-vรญ-dแปฅ-nรขng-cao-hiแปn-thแป-thแปi-gian-thแปฑc#6. Vรญ dแปฅ nรขng cao: Hiแปn thแป thแปi gian thแปฑc":"","7-cรกch-gแบฏn-sแปฑ-kiแปn-trong-html-khรดng-khuyแบฟn-khรญch#7. Cรกch gแบฏn sแปฑ kiแปn trong HTML (khรดng khuyแบฟn khรญch)":"Bแบกn cรณ thแป gแบฏn sแปฑ kiแปn trแปฑc tiแบฟp trong HTML:\n\u003cbutton onclick=\"alert('Xin chรo!')\"\u003eBแบฅm vรo ฤรขy\u003c/button\u003e\rTuy nhiรชn, cรกch nรy khรณ quแบฃn lรฝ khi dแปฑ รกn lแปn.\nCรกch dรนng addEventListener() (แป trรชn) lร chuแบฉn hฦกn.","8-tรณm-tแบฏt-kiแบฟn-thแปฉc#8. Tรณm tแบฏt kiแบฟn thแปฉc":"Khรกi niแปm Mรด tแบฃ DOM Mรด hรฌnh cรขy ฤแบกi diแปn cho tรi liแปu HTML getElementById / querySelector Dรนng ฤแป truy cแบญp phแบงn tแปญ addEventListener Dรนng ฤแป lแบฏng nghe sแปฑ kiแปn Event Hรnh ฤแปng cแปงa ngฦฐแปi dรนng (click, input, โฆ)","bรi-8-dom-vร-sแปฑ-kiแปn--lรm-web-tฦฐฦกng-tรกc#Bรi 8. DOM vร Sแปฑ kiแปn โ Lรm web tฦฐฦกng tรกc":"Bรi 8. DOM vร Sแปฑ kiแปn โ Lรm web tฦฐฦกng tรกc","cรกch-1-getelementbyid#Cรกch 1: getElementById()":"Truy cแบญp phแบงn tแปญ thรดng qua id.\nconst title = document.getElementById(\"title\"); title.textContent = \"Xin chรo, JavaScript!\";","cรกch-2-queryselector#Cรกch 2: querySelector()":"Truy cแบญp phแบงn tแปญ bแบฑng CSS selector (rแบฅt linh hoแบกt).\nconst desc = document.querySelector(\".desc\"); desc.style.color = \"blue\";","cรกch-3-queryselectorall#Cรกch 3: querySelectorAll()":"Trแบฃ vแป tแบฅt cแบฃ cรกc phแบงn tแปญ khแปp selector (NodeList).\nconst items = document.querySelectorAll(\"p\"); items.forEach(item =\u003e item.style.fontWeight = \"bold\");","cแบฅu-trรบc-dom-sแบฝ-trรดng-nhฦฐ-thแบฟ-nรy#Cแบฅu trรบc DOM sแบฝ trรดng nhฦฐ thแบฟ nรy:":"graph TD\rA[Document] --\u003e B[html]\rB --\u003e C[head]\rB --\u003e D[body]\rD --\u003e E[h1 id=\"title\"]\rD --\u003e F[p class=\"desc\"]\rJavaScript cรณ thแป โฤi vรoโ cรขy DOM ฤแป thay ฤแปi bแบฅt kแปณ phแบงn tแปญ nรo.","html#HTML:":"\u003ch2\u003eThay ฤแปi mรu nแปn\u003c/h2\u003e \u003cbutton id=\"btn\"\u003eฤแปi mรu\u003c/button\u003e","html-1#HTML:":"\u003cp\u003eGiแป hiแปn tแบกi: \u003cspan id=\"clock\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","javascript#JavaScript:":"const btn = document.getElementById(\"btn\"); btn.addEventListener(\"click\", function() { document.body.style.backgroundColor = document.body.style.backgroundColor === \"lightblue\" ? \"white\" : \"lightblue\"; });\rMแปi lแบงn bแบกn bแบฅm nรบt, trang sแบฝ ฤแปi mรu nแปn giแปฏa trแบฏng vร xanh nhแบกt.","javascript-1#JavaScript:":"function updateClock() { const now = new Date(); const time = now.toLocaleTimeString(); document.getElementById(\"clock\").textContent = time; } setInterval(updateClock, 1000);\rKแบฟt quแบฃ: ฤแปng hแป chแบกy tแปซng giรขy ngay trรชn trang web","kแบฟt-luแบญn#Kแบฟt luแบญn":"DOM vร sแปฑ kiแปn lร trรกi tim cแปงa lแบญp trรฌnh web bแบฑng JavaScript, nhแป